Goal Representation:
Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['Cut the chicken into pieces, then put it back in the fridge.']

def inside_fridge(x: item):
    symbol in_fridge=exists fridge: item : is_fridge(fridge) and inside(x, fridge)
    return in_fridge

behavior secure_chicken(chicken:item, fridge:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(fridge) # Ensure the fridge is closed after placing the chicken inside

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken)
        # Select the chicken

        bind cutting_board: item where:
            is_cutting_board(cutting_board)
        # Identify a cutting board

        bind knife: item where:
            is_knife(knife)
        # Identify a knife
        
        bind fridge: item where:
            is_fridge(fridge)
        # Select the fridge
        
        if not cut(chicken):
            achieve close(cutting_board, chicken)
            achieve close(knife, chicken)
            achieve_once inhand(knife) 
            achieve cut(chicken)
        
        achieve inside(chicken, fridge)
        
        secure_chicken(chicken, fridge)

Reset goals: The sub-goals are: 
['Cut the chicken into pieces and put it back in the fridge.']

behavior cut_chicken(chicken:item, knife:item, cutting_board:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inhand(knife)
        achieve cut(chicken)

behavior store_in_fridge(chicken:item, fridge:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(chicken, fridge)

behavior close_the_fridge_door(fridge:item):
    body:
        achieve closed(fridge)

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken)
        # Select chicken
        bind knife: item where:
            is_knife(knife)
        # Select a knife
        bind cutting_board: item where:
            is_cutting_board(cutting_board)
        # Select a cutting board
        bind fridge: item where:
            is_fridge(fridge)
        # Select a fridge

        cut_chicken(chicken, knife, cutting_board)
        store_in_fridge(chicken, fridge)
        close_the_fridge_door(fridge)
